description:
Trusted by generations for a streak-free shine, Windex Original Glass Cleaner is a great solution for lightening, brightening and sparkling your home.

Windex Glass Cleaner starts working on dirt, grime, fingerprints and other messes even before you wipe.

Works great on: Glass, mirrors, countertops, appliances, sealed granite, sealed marble, laminate, stainless steel.
 
Give Life a Sparkle with Windex cleaners! 

Perfect for cleaning glass, windows and more!

Removes fingerprints, smudges and smears

Leaves a streak-free shine!

Lightens and brightens your home leaving it sparkling clean

Starts working on smudges and smears even before you wipe
name: Windex Glass Cleaner Trigger 500mL
